Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I know I've come too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wish to work for Tsurukame Travel—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, for your esteemed company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna throw one of your hissyfits again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You lying, no-account girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:59.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a very public, very firm declaration yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! You can do it, Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we'd go to Yugoslavia together, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:09.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to win the World Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:15.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and go to Saikai University with Beanpole, and that's final!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:28.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I've been chosen as a training player for the Yugoslavia World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:37.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get to play in any matches,\N but I can still go to Yugoslavia with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:44.47,epTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.3\be1\pos(320,400)\3c&H3548D5&\c&H4137FD&}Fujiko's First Training Camp!{\c&H3238F7&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good night to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:16.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're going to the World Championships with Yawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for making this food for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:30.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, eat up, Beanpole, while I eat {\i1}and{\i0\fscx130} {\r\}drink. {beer = Hell's Wheels}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a toast, Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:43.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san, I'm very moved by all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.54,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to the World Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Inokuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:07.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what gives? The sake will go stale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:07.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.75,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Training camp will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:34.39,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to build up my strength so that I won't hold Inokuma-san back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.52,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what am I supposed to say to Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:51.81,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to the World Championships, and I'm not going to training camp either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be a training player for the World Championships?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful, Fujiko-san! Truly wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:32.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't believe I'm going to Yugoslavia with Inokuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:41.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's not a dream! You're strong, Fujiko-san. Very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I too want to be a judo competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:52.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanazono-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:06:01.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that you'll become really good and go beyond my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Inokuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:15.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Back at the tournament, if it hadn't been for your support, I would've lost for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fujiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:28.03,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: All Sports News
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.74,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The training camp for the World Championships is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.76,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Teleshikova from the USSR and Jody from Canada:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:40.54,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,we have the two main players, which leaves Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:45.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:52.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuni-chan made a very special lunch for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:57.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Doesn't it look yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:03.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked very hard on it just for you, Kosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use that time to do some actual work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be so bashful, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We know you're thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit showing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now those look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. They're all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.85,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Magazine: Izu-Ito\NFun in the Hot Spring Steam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsurukame Travel's Cordial Hot Springs Tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you seen the TV commercials?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:08:01.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Travel with Tsurukame. Cordial Tsurukame."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see they have heaps of good eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a hot spring ain't such a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:17.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Practically everybody is going on those trips,\N and all the popular hot springs are booked solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's no need to worry, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was working as a travel agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:28.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could easily get us a good room, along with delicious food...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:33.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be working for who? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I was just saying "what if."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, "what if."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't having your "what ifs" or chive liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:46.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing judo at Saikai U should be the only thing on your mind, you nitwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do something nice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna do something nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:54.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,then play judo, become the world champ, win the gold medal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and get the National Achievement Award!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to take you to a hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna go to a hot spring, do it on your honeymoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. I spent my honeymoon with Kaneko at the Atami Hot Springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidentally, it was the night before the outbreak of the Pacific War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I've heard that story a hundred times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.59,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'm going to tell Fujiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll be treating you, Inokuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:07.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You came along when I applied for my passport, even though you were busy practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must tell me what it's like inside an airplane and all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first trip overseas, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I've been running a lot, so I'm pretty hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Inokuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:29.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be eating, since training camp's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! Look! It's a guidebook for Yugoslavia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.61,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Book: Eastern Europe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm checking for what to bring back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugoslavia has so many delicious foods!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's Madera's sarma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It says there's no point going to Yugoslavia if you don't try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so good. I'm definitely going to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ražnjići, ćevapčići,}Raznjici, cevapcici, Bosnian hotpot... {font lacks accented c's!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.84,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is... um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:22.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san, do you need to go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. It's nothing to be embarrassed about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:32.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go! It's not good to hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to speak to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:52.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only able to talk about this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:58.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I lost due to that referee's call, I cried when I got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:11.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I smiled in front of everyone,\N but actually, I was really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:18.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only able to say something so shameful to you, Inokuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:24.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's Yugoslavia or Saikai U, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:31.35,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: World Championship Training Camp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:36.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin our training camp for the World Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the director, Yanagizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:46.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to your coaches and get into your best condition for the day of the championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.54,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\bord0.6\pos(50,228)\blur1.1\fad(0,479)}Translation: kokujin-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.54,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\bord0.6\pos(50,253)\blur1.1\fad(0,479)}Editing: Collectr
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.54,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\bord0.6\pos(50,278)\blur1.1\fad(0,479)}Encoding: Skr
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.96,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\pos(50,228)\bord0.6\blur1.1\fad(479,0)}Timing: Juggen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.96,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\pos(50,253)\bord0.6\blur1.1\fad(479,0)}DVD Provider: CP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.96,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\pos(50,278)\bord0.6\blur1.1\fad(479,0)}QC Team: CP, Mamo-chan, sangofe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.96,logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs22\b0\pos(50,303)\bord0.6\blur1.1\fad(479,0)}\h                  Juggen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:41.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it appears that Inokuma Yawara is leaving. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We {\i1}are{\i0\fscx130} {\r\}done with our morning training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one tough chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She left me completely immobile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:57.55,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She was dressed pretty smartly. Where is she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.01,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Parlor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so glad you came to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:52.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though if you'd asked, we would have met you anywhere you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wouldn't think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Training camp must be stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw it on TV and in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking on the world, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Taking on the world is no easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:10.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We would like to be the top travel agency in the world someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's top travel agency? I'd like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:26.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what became of your attempt to turn your grandfather around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but I will convince him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So can you give me a little more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:50.83,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Travel Consultation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:58.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're looking for the best hotel in Yugoslavia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:21.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking how splendid it would be to travel to Yugoslavia with someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I'll be traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:40.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not just this time. I always travel alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's because I work too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a soldier needs a break once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you, I feel more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:05.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Why don't we go out to dinner or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:07.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamatsuri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yawara-san, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Inokuma Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:53.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute! Why that company?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.65,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've done much better for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0\fscx130} {\r}the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your transfer to Saikai U?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to Saikai U.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then what about judo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Tsurukame Travel even have a team?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't? Then how will you play judo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:22.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, all you talk about is judo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:26.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-san has had enough of judo, what with the World Championships coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:29.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk about judo over her noon break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back to camp. It's time for my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:48.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait! Why are you bending over backwards to get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Must you always be the aggressive reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:57.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before that my first career choice was to be a travel agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you want to work using your own abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll be able to see the world at a travel agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great? I admire your motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually have one more reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:17.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,that working at a travel agency would make it easier for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,to search for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I work at a travel agency, there's a chance I'll meet someone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:34.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,who gave my dad a boarding pass or saw him at one of his destinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's good thinking.\N Don't you agree, Matsuda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:45.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'm really going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then I'll take her to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:05.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reuniting her with her dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:08.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kazamatsuri!\N Tell me where Kojiro-san is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kojiro-san right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:14.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojiro-san is Sayaka-san's coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:19.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let Yawara-san see him, how do you think she'll react?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why didn't you stop him from becoming her coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-san practically begged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I could've stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:34.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to pick up the check, but forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay for your own coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:39.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All Sports{\i0\fscx130} {\r\}really does pay you peanuts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay for Yawara-san's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're paid below market, so I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:50.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:51.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One more time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:16.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go spar with the guys on the national team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:25.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more round! I think I'm beginning to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:27.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, deux, trois...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:34.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, deux, trois...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:38.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Ito Fujiko I've been hearing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:40.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's pretty good, Yamashita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:45.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is she good, it's a waste of good talent to use her as just a training player!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Inokuma Jigoro, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deux!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:54.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it taste great? \NThis is Beanpole's home brew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her tea is as good as her judo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:01.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, only because I taught her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has the height and the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:07.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be evenly matched with a foreign opponent. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:12.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Director Yanagizawa, have you decided on the free-weight player yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:17.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet. However, we'd really like it to be Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:19.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Trois!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:22.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:23.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His head took the entire blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right, Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:26.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, he's out like a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:35.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Oh gosh, wait... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:43.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-O-R-R-Y!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:52.93,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: The Barcelona Olympics in {\c&H5C74FF&}320{\r} Days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally going to Yugoslavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:22:58.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san's really relishing this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:00.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she should enjoy it while it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:02.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:05.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This tatsuta-age is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:08.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're up to something, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:12.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can expect some very interesting developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:13.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Opening Act of the Yugoslavia World Championships!
